1
00:00:14,259 --> 00:00:14,859
Come on.

2
00:00:15,539 --> 00:00:17,059
Let's see

3
00:00:17,059 --> 00:00:18,579
what treasures Mr. Gao has brought.

4
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:28,140
The tribute from the East Sea, a blood jade coral.

5
00:00:28,620 --> 00:00:29,859
The core is hollow,

6
00:00:31,879 --> 00:00:33,979
with strange colored powder.

7
00:00:34,840 --> 00:00:36,560
It's suspected to be damaged

8
00:00:37,740 --> 00:00:39,619
due to improper care.

9
00:00:39,820 --> 00:00:41,460
The spirit has been lost.

10
00:00:41,820 --> 00:00:42,700
Take it away.

11
00:00:44,259 --> 00:00:45,179
My lord!

12
00:00:45,299 --> 00:00:46,299
Please spare me!

13
00:00:46,500 --> 00:00:47,020
My lord, please!

14
00:00:47,020 --> 00:00:48,420
Execute!

15
00:00:48,420 --> 00:00:49,420
My lord, please!

16
00:00:49,539 --> 00:00:50,780
My lord, please!

17
00:00:50,780 --> 00:00:51,200
My lord!

18
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:52,740
How imposing the Grand Steward is!

19
00:00:52,780 --> 00:00:53,979
My lord, please!

20
00:00:54,579 --> 00:00:55,579
My lord!

21
00:00:55,899 --> 00:00:57,179
Please spare me!

22
00:00:57,479 --> 00:00:58,380
My lord.

23
00:01:01,740 --> 00:01:02,700
Envoy Bai Zhen,

24
00:01:02,939 --> 00:01:04,140
you've returned.

25
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:24,400
I heard your journey was perilous,

26
00:01:25,219 --> 00:01:26,939
and you nearly met with an accident.

27
00:01:27,540 --> 00:01:30,939
You should take better care of yourself.

28
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:32,840
No need for your concern.

29
00:01:33,900 --> 00:01:35,299
Whoever wishes to harm me,

30
00:01:35,620 --> 00:01:36,980
I am well aware.

31
00:01:37,219 --> 00:01:37,700
Yes.

32
00:01:38,099 --> 00:01:38,859
Yes.

33
00:01:43,140 --> 00:01:44,379
This is

34
00:01:44,980 --> 00:01:47,620
Lady An appointed by the Queen Mother.

35
00:01:50,260 --> 00:01:51,739
According to the Bai Zhen Decree,

36
00:01:52,019 --> 00:01:53,459
when a lady joins the division,

37
00:01:53,700 --> 00:01:57,140
she must be carefully verified.

38
00:02:07,540 --> 00:02:08,379
Behave yourself.

39
00:02:19,580 --> 00:02:22,580
Take off the handkerchief on your hand

40
00:02:23,300 --> 00:02:25,180
to avoid any suspicion of smuggling.

41
00:02:28,539 --> 00:02:29,460
[No stab wounds,]

42
00:02:30,020 --> 00:02:31,419
[just some scratches.]

43
00:02:32,580 --> 00:02:34,340
[Could it be that she and the madwoman Su Luoyao]

44
00:02:34,780 --> 00:02:36,060
[are truly not the same person?]

45
00:02:39,939 --> 00:02:41,900
Truly a skilled hand.

46
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,199
Let me

47
00:02:44,699 --> 00:02:46,180
take a good look

48
00:02:46,180 --> 00:02:48,580
at your physique and bone structure.

49
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:55,979
The person I brought here

50
00:02:57,659 --> 00:02:59,460
is not someone you are qualified to examine.

51
00:03:00,500 --> 00:03:01,020
Yes.
Yes.

52
00:03:02,060 --> 00:03:04,419
Since she's escorted by Envoy Baizhen herself,

53
00:03:04,419 --> 00:03:05,659
there must be no problem.

54
00:03:05,819 --> 00:03:06,379
Guards,

55
00:03:06,460 --> 00:03:08,819
escort Lady An to the Pavilion.

56
00:03:36,219 --> 00:03:38,340
You talented painter,

57
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:42,580
let's see how long you can keep this up.

58
00:04:49,779 --> 00:04:51,100
Finally finished.

59
00:04:54,500 --> 00:04:55,139
An Rao,

60
00:04:56,180 --> 00:04:57,180
did you get treated unfairly?

61
00:04:59,699 --> 00:05:01,180
Today, it's just ten paintings.

62
00:05:01,740 --> 00:05:02,540
Tomorrow,

63
00:05:02,620 --> 00:05:04,300
who knows what else she'll throw at us?

64
00:05:10,060 --> 00:05:11,019
It's the middle of the night.

65
00:05:12,779 --> 00:05:13,220
Don't be afraid.

66
00:05:14,180 --> 00:05:14,980
Your painting

67
00:05:16,379 --> 00:05:17,699
isn't that easy to take.

68
00:05:17,939 --> 00:05:20,300
What do you mean by that?

69
00:05:21,540 --> 00:05:22,480
Someone's dead!

70
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:38,319
It's a painting demon!

71
00:05:38,660 --> 00:05:39,740
[It's the demon coming for our lives!]

72
00:05:39,939 --> 00:05:40,839
[It's the demon coming for our lives!]
Shut up!

73
00:05:54,019 --> 00:05:55,259
This is the work of An Rao.

74
00:06:13,579 --> 00:06:15,019
The scent of medicine in the blood

75
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:17,100
is from Su Luoyao.

76
00:06:25,540 --> 00:06:26,540
On the night of the full moon,

77
00:06:27,079 --> 00:06:28,439
the Silken Thread poison is about to take effect.

78
00:06:28,779 --> 00:06:30,420
Present the Baozhen Decree.

79
00:06:51,100 --> 00:06:52,220
What's going on here?

80
00:06:52,660 --> 00:06:54,220
It seems to be the work of a painting demon.

81
00:06:55,939 --> 00:06:56,779
A painting demon?

82
00:06:58,379 --> 00:06:58,980
Changfeng,

83
00:06:59,699 --> 00:07:00,759
since when do you also

84
00:07:00,759 --> 00:07:02,420
believe in such nonsense?

85
00:07:08,180 --> 00:07:09,100
Investigate this.

86
00:07:09,379 --> 00:07:10,339
In the Treasure House,

87
00:07:10,819 --> 00:07:11,699
no one is allowed

88
00:07:11,699 --> 00:07:13,060
to act recklessly

89
00:07:13,879 --> 00:07:15,259
in the name of ghosts and gods.

90
00:07:19,459 --> 00:07:20,180
Who

91
00:07:20,699 --> 00:07:21,860
created this painting?

92
00:07:38,259 --> 00:07:40,379
This was meant to be a torture device,

93
00:07:41,180 --> 00:07:43,100
but the artist injured their finger.

94
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,160
Oh no.

95
00:07:45,139 --> 00:07:46,620
It's just an eye.

96
00:07:46,740 --> 00:07:47,740
It doesn't matter.

97
00:07:48,740 --> 00:07:49,699
What do you think?

98
00:07:52,300 --> 00:07:53,459
I really don't know anything.

99
00:07:54,779 --> 00:07:56,459
Tonight, I was locked in the gallery

100
00:07:56,740 --> 00:07:58,300
by the head chamberlain to paint.

101
00:08:01,819 --> 00:08:03,699
I don't like to hear lies.

102
00:08:04,420 --> 00:08:05,620
Tell me the truth,

103
00:08:06,220 --> 00:08:07,220
and I'll spare you.

104
00:08:07,579 --> 00:08:08,379
How about that?

105
00:08:08,660 --> 00:08:09,620
I don't know.

106
00:08:09,980 --> 00:08:10,980
I really don't know.

107
00:08:11,300 --> 00:08:12,100
Lady An,

108
00:08:13,699 --> 00:08:15,339
don't be so ungrateful.

109
00:08:16,899 --> 00:08:17,579
Report!

110
00:08:18,379 --> 00:08:18,779
My lord,
we've checked,

111
00:08:20,019 --> 00:08:21,139
and found no traces left.

112
00:08:21,899 --> 00:08:22,339
It's like

113
00:08:22,740 --> 00:08:24,180
done by a ghost.

114
00:08:24,259 --> 00:08:25,100
A bunch of useless people.

115
00:08:25,980 --> 00:08:27,100
I'll check it myself.

116
00:08:27,879 --> 00:08:28,500
My Lord,

117
00:08:28,699 --> 00:08:30,660
the Queen Mother said she wanted to see the painting tomorrow.

118
00:08:32,700 --> 00:08:33,860
Let her speak.

119
00:08:34,019 --> 00:08:34,539
Yes.

120
00:08:55,740 --> 00:08:56,139
[Remember,]

121
00:08:56,860 --> 00:08:57,659
[no matter how difficult,]

122
00:08:58,100 --> 00:08:58,639
[hold on.]

123
00:09:00,539 --> 00:09:01,539
[I'll come to get you.]

124
00:09:13,419 --> 00:09:14,100
Su Luoyao!

125
00:09:18,820 --> 00:09:19,580
Su Luoyao!

126
00:09:25,460 --> 00:09:26,220
Su Luoyao!

127
00:09:27,179 --> 00:09:28,139
I know you're here.

128
00:09:46,860 --> 00:09:48,220
Eager to see your master, huh?

129
00:09:48,899 --> 00:09:50,700
Tonight, the case of the painting demon

130
00:09:50,700 --> 00:09:51,740
was your doing, right?

131
00:09:52,460 --> 00:09:53,740
Hand over the antidote,

132
00:09:54,659 --> 00:09:56,379
or I'll reveal the truth.

133
00:10:13,679 --> 00:10:14,460
Little slave,

134
00:10:14,899 --> 00:10:15,279
have you forgotten

135
00:10:15,279 --> 00:10:16,580
how he hurt you?

136
00:10:17,980 --> 00:10:19,019
He's dead.

137
00:10:20,340 --> 00:10:21,299
Aren't you happy?

138
00:10:33,700 --> 00:10:34,980
Using pain to break illusions.

139
00:10:37,559 --> 00:10:38,759
Smart move.

140
00:10:41,460 --> 00:10:43,259
You think you can control me?

141
00:10:44,019 --> 00:10:45,860
Being my slave isn't so bad.

142
00:10:46,539 --> 00:10:47,539
The gods won't save you,

143
00:10:48,179 --> 00:10:48,980
but I can.

144
00:10:50,179 --> 00:10:51,580
I can give you everything

145
00:10:52,259 --> 00:10:53,100
the Xie family can't.

146
00:10:53,779 --> 00:10:56,639
Like the position of the Baozhen Decree.

147
00:10:57,639 --> 00:10:58,980
You're acting like a lunatic,

148
00:10:59,179 --> 00:11:00,899
always causing trouble.

149
00:11:01,299 --> 00:11:02,820
Now you've sent An Rao to the Dept.

150
00:11:02,820 --> 00:11:03,899
She can't even protect herself.

151
00:11:04,379 --> 00:11:05,419
Why should I trust you?

152
00:11:09,620 --> 00:11:10,500
Lunatics

153
00:11:11,340 --> 00:11:13,740
have their own ways.

154
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:22,440
Tomorrow, at the blessing banquet

155
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:25,600
of the Baozhen Dept.,

156
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,240
just wait and see.
